{"tid":1755361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有區選素人","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T15:05:01.000Z","uid":112055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8ee31a6d529068b0ec2979fcd963acb7559a5f","tid":1755361,"uid":112055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"黎緊四年你地有個新任務了，請用行動證明唔係剩係建制先識做地區野。請好好利用區議員資料幫助文宣，拉攏建制鐵票。整左街燈唔洗出poster打飛機，請用fb,ig分享就夠。做多少少老人院野，有時間探下婆婆咁。地區野要做，政治野更加要做。取他人之長，建制之所以長期坐住個位係因為啲老人家單純係睇邊個對佢好架咋，請額外用少少力打爆佢地。<br />\n記住啊手足，切忌赢左一次就驕傲。<br />\n重點係，五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"f8ea322bdf5bb93b1c1aac9c457ccd5268a492a5","tid":1755361,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b92a41809c9a7589be756fcf0ff85f46d0155a8","tid":1755361,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:21:10.000Z","msg":"真 社區工作係好重要 希望大家幫下佐敦嗰位陳議員 佢幾乎0團隊0經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179fc1bf055a05bdb67515993d36992ea773d115","tid":1755361,"uid":38279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHwbXOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHwbXOQ.png&h=551fea42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55b68a51565d584900dcac963c1cf1bfde146b39","tid":1755361,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:41:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釋放義士</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ab88a71b905d506e7a4f84e4aa2c1c3397a4011","tid":1755361,"uid":112055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:05:01.000Z","msg":"五"}]}